reviews: It was a pretty perfect fit. I’m usually a men’s small but I ordered a men’s medium (thank God I did) because I wanted it to be a bit baggy. Unfortunately, it wasn’t baggy at all and fit me like a small would. So if you want a baggier hoodie, I’d recommend ordering 2 sizes up.
